## Remarks

The path attribute can not end in `\` unless the path is the root value of `\`. 

Valid path values (yaml encoded) include:
- `\\`
- `\\ExampleFolder`
- `\\Nested\\Example Folder`

The value of `\\ExampleFolder\\` would be invalid.

