The Azure DevOps UI uses roles to assign permissions for the Library.

| Role          | Allowed Permissions    |
| ------------- | ---------------------- |
| Reader        | View                   |
| Creator       | View, Create           |
| User          | View, Use              |
| Administrator | View, Use, Administer  |

