## Roles

The Azure DevOps UI uses roles to assign permissions for variable groups.

| Role          | Allow Permissions      |
| ------------- | ---------------------- |
| Reader        | View                   |
| User          | View, Use              |
| Administrator | View, Use, Administer  |


## Relevant Links

